===Governor&#x27;s Cup===
Regular season champions:
*1996–97 – New Mexico Scorpions
*1997–98 – Fort Worth Brahmas
*1998–99 – Shreveport Mudbugs
*1999–00 – Central Texas Stampede
*2000–01 – Tupelo T-Rex

