* Inoue Genzaburō
* Harada Sanosuke
* Saitō Hajime
* Sasazuka Minezō
* Hayashi Shintarō
* Shimada Kai
* Kawashima Katsuji
* Katsurayama Takehachirō
* Tani Sanjūrō
* Mishina Chūji
* Aridōshi Kango
* Matsubara Chūji
* Iki Hachirō
* Nakamura Kingo
* Ozeki Yashirō
* Shukuin Ryozō
* Sasaki Kuranosuke
* Kawai Kisaburō
* Sakai Hyōgo
* Kiuchi Mineta
* Matsumoto Kijirō
* Takeuchi Gentarō
* Kōndō Shūhei

